workshop.internal.entities

Class WorkshopEntityType

  • java.lang.Object
    • workshop.internal.entities.WorkshopEntityAbstract
      • workshop.internal.entities.Trackable
        • workshop.internal.entities.WorkshopEntityType
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    java.io.Serializable, java.lang.Comparable<WorkshopEntity>, WorkshopEntity

    @Entity
public class WorkshopEntityType
extends Trackable
    The class is the container for WorkshopEntity types (classes names). All the available WorkshopEntity class names are available through WorkshopEntity.workshopEntitiesNames. This class can contain only those exact names for giving access to the according WorkshopEntity in conjunction with PermissionType.
